== Documentation ==
This is to be used when edits to a page may need proofreading.
=== Example Usage ===
<nowiki>{{Proofread|Section 2 needs to be checked}}</nowiki>

will make:
{{Proofread|Section 2 needs to be checked|nocat=1}}

=== Template parameters ===
{| class="wikitable"
|-
! Name !! Variable !! Description
|-
| Reason || <code>1</code>|| Gives the reason as to what needs proofreading.
|}
<templatedata>
{
	"params": {
		"1": {
			"label": "Reason",
			"description": "What needs to be proofread?",
			"type": "string",
			"suggested": true
		}
	},
	"description": "For when a page/section needs proofreading"
}
</templatedata>
